					"type": 23,
					"value": "Lae'zel died in the tutorial. Her body was found on the beach (remember that bodies can be moved though). Player revived her.\r\nThe flag ORI_LaezelRecruitment_State_CrashVersionInitiated is set upon loading WLD_Main_A, when this version of the recruitment is activated."
